.\" Manpage for gitsubmodule.
.\" Contact eng.abdelrazzak@gmail.com to correct errors or typos.
.TH man 1 "20 August 2013" "1.0" "gitsubmodule man page"
.SH NAME
    gitsubmodule \- add update and remove opertaions. complimentary to git submodule command.
.SH SYNOPSIS
     gitsubmodule [options | options[args]]
.SH DESCRIPTION
    this script easen up some of the common hard or long  to do operations in git submodule
    like updating the submodules or removing them
.SH EXAMPLES
    gitsubmodule update ner
        prompt the user to update submodules that matches this search
        ex. nerdTree, nerdCommenter
    gitsubmodule update help
        display help of the update

    gitsubmodule remove 
        prompt the user to remove one of the available submodules

    gitsubmodule -d ~/.vim -r nerd
        show the matched submodules in the vim ex(nerdTree,nerdCommenter)
        if only one of them is available ,prompt removing it and commit 
.SH SEE ALSO
    git(1), git submodule(1)
.SH BUGS
      No known bugs.
